glass-budget (1.0.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix critical Debian package installation issues
  * Add preinst script to create directories before installation
  * Improve error handling in postinst script with better validation
  * Fix file permission issues during package build process
  * Add safety checks for file existence in debian/rules
  * Update systemd service ReadWritePaths configuration
  * Simplify dependency management to reduce conflicts
  * Add validation for required system commands
  * Improve service startup error handling and reporting
  * Add package validation test script

